              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "D4PI",
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " This detector consists of a 12inch*12inch",
                "NaI(Tl) monocrystal of cylindrical shape with a",
                "borehole  of 35 mm diameter along its axis.  The target",
                "is placed at the centre of the crystal, which covers  a",
                "solid angle of almost 98%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "By authors.  The main advantage of using such a summing",
                "detector is that the response of the NaI(Tl) crystal",
                "leads predominantly to a single peak, called sum peak,",
                "at the sum of the energies of the cascading",
                "transitions."
              ]
            }
